Package com.cafean.jobstream.common

Class SubmitContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.jobstream.common.SubmitContext
  • public class SubmitContext
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple wrapper object that encapsulates the information necessary for the submission of a Stream Manager or Execution Wrapper job to a Platform Module. This object is used in the place of separate arguments to insulate the PlatformModule API against minor additions to the information provided to the module at submit time.
